      • combine

        public static List<ProcessData> combine(List<ProcessData> metrics)
        Combines a list of ProcessData into single instances grouped by individual process. This method takes a weighted average of all fields based on deltaMillis.
        Parameters:
        metrics - list of Process metrics
        Returns:
        list of aggregated ProcessData instances, one for each unique process
